	<h2>I love making terrariums. I can’t stop making terrariums. My home is becoming one big terrarium. Time to share these little creations...with you!</h2>
	<p>
		Terrariums provide a platform upon which my idealistic dreams can come true!  Taking pieces from the environment at large and manipulating them into a small container where they will thrive and establish their own, separate environment is fascinating and inspiring to me.  
